27:35.306 --> 27:35.706
Guarantee it.

27:36.687 --> 27:38.549
Most divisive sermon I've ever preached next Sunday.

27:42.333 --> 27:43.174
We're going to talk about that.

27:45.176 --> 27:46.738
But who guaranteed you next Sunday?

27:48.930 --> 27:50.392
Nobody's guaranteed me next Sunday.

27:52.676 --> 27:55.341
And so give your life to Christ today.

27:58.426 --> 28:01.712
You've been listening to a message from First Baptist Church, Wichita Falls.

